SUMMARY:Impromptu CoffeeTue- LP Speckled Hen Coffee (26F) -- RSVP Required
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Bicycle Club (LBC) Meetup\nRide Leader: Rick Zook\nC
 offeeTue rides:\n• A rotating start location\, not a school\n• A prede
 termined route\n• 25+/- mile routes\n• 13 to 15 mph average pace\n• 
 Usually no sweep\n• “short” stop for refreshment/coffee mid-route at
  [Speckled Hen Coffee](https://www.speckledhencoffee.com/).\n\nClick for [
 Ride with GPS](https://routes.lancasterbikeclub.net/cue/lp-speckled-hen-co
 ffee-26f/)\nOne of my favorite routes for early in the season. Let's keep 
 the pace and stay together.\n\nHelmets are mandatory. No ear buds. Please 
 bring water and a basic repair kit (spare tube\, tire levers\, pump/CO2 in
 flator).\n\nTo eliminate passing around a pen and paper waiver\, we requir
 e LBC Club membership and Meetup RSVP below to join this ride.\n\nBeing on
  Meetup does not mean you are a club member. [Join here](https://www.lanca
 sterbikeclub.net/content.aspx?page_id=60&club_id=257148).\n\nYour RSVP is 
 your agreement to abide by the club's [Code of Conduct](https://lancbikecl
 ub.clubexpress.com/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=323984
 ) \,\n[Rules of the Road](https://lancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/content.asp
 x?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=325159) \, and [Ride Waiver](https:/
 /lancasterbikeclub.net/docs.ashx?id=454318)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/lancaster-bicycle-club/events/3139803
 11/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260327T124605Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260327T124605Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
