 tay in one group. Cyclists may pedal at their own comfortable paces. Pleas
 e be supportive of the other cyclists to avoid anyone biking alone or bein
 g dropped off the back of the last group.\n\nClick for [Ride with GPS](htt
 ps://ridewithgps.com/routes/54305292)\n\nHelmets are mandatory. No ear bud
 s. Please bring water and a basic repair kit (spare tube\, tire levers\, p
 ump/CO2 inflator).\n\nTo eliminate passing around a pen and paper waiver\,
  we require LBC Club membership and Meetup RSVP below to join this ride.\n
 \nBeing on Meetup does not mean you are a club member. [Join here](https:/
